```plantuml
@startuml hyper-prog_hasses

actor WebServer as "Web Server"
participant "hasses (Main)" as hasses
participant "epoll" as epoll
participant "ClientManager (cdata)" as cdata
participant "SSEHandler (chat)" as chat
participant "I/O Manager (cio)" as cio
participant Client as "SSE Client"

WebServer -> hasses : Send message (via FIFO/TCP)
hasses -> cdata : Route message to clients
cdata -> chat : Format as SSE event
chat -> cio : Write to client socket(s)
cio -> epoll : Monitor socket readiness
epoll -> cio : Notify when writable
cio -> Client : Send SSE event
Client -> cio : Keep connection open
cio -> epoll : Continue monitoring

@enduml
```